settings.heading: Sign up for the FREE ticket drop
settings.text:
Fatboy Slim is returning to Enter Gallery!

On Friday 1st March, we’re celebrating the launch of Fatboy Slim by Jessica van der Weert: 10 Years Photographing The Legend – a collection of new artworks depicting the superstar DJ from the photographer behind his most iconic imagery.

Join us from 6.30-8pm at the Private View to meet Jessica van der Weert and to experience this new collection for the first time. Fatboy Slim will be in attendance, playing records from his own collection.

Tickets to this event will be snapped up quickly. Sign up to our emails be notified when tickets are released.
